<plot>This video shows the positive impact alternative trading organizations (ATOs) have in developing countries. It centers on women in remote communities in Zimbabwe who weave baskets for sale through alternative trading organizations in developed countries. The basket trade helps the women feed and clothe their families, and improve their craft and business skills.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?070176</url></doc>
